spec_data.Name: perl-Test-Dependencies
spec_data.Description:
Makes sure that all of the modules that are 'use'd are listed in the
Makefile.PL as dependencies.

It has two styles: light, which is fast but confusable; and heavy, which takes
more time but is more accurate.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 04:38:57 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Ensure that your Makefile.PL specifies all module dependencies
